StreamUIManager:  > is called on onResume();
                > Check SharedPrefrences for stream status
                > Transact Stream fragment accordingly
                > Subscribe For Player(Streaming) Events(stop,error,pause,play)

StreamFragment: > onAttach()- get Stream Info From shared Pref. and update to views

StreamPref    : > saves stream status
                > get/set stream info

StreamerCallbackListener: > contains method to inform different state of player

Streamer Is old Streamer
